data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ***SELLER IS OFFERING $3,000 TOWARDS CLOSING COST*** Home currently has FHA ASSUMABLE mortgage at 2.5%. Take advantage of this opportunity for a great rate! Welcome home to PARADISE at luxurious TOSCANA ISLES! You will feel like you are on vacation year-round in this gorgeous resort style, maintenance free, 24-hr. gated community. This lovely home is immaculate and better than new with many UPGRADES!! Walking up to the home you will notice features such as lush tropical landscaping, brick paver driveway and a tile roof. This Cottage Series “Brighton” floor plan was constructed in 2021 and offers 1544 sq. ft., 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, plus a DEN. As you step inside, you will feel a sense of calmness in this light and bright open living concept home. All of the main living areas offer tile flooring, 9 ft. ceilings with crown molding, 8-ft. interior doors, smart home technology, serene color pallet, with ceiling fans and plantation shutters throughout. The elegant kitchen offers quartz countertops, designer tile backsplash, and decorative pendant lights. The kitchen also offers an abundance of gray “shaker style” cabinets, stainless steel appliances, pantry and a generous breakfast bar. Just off the kitchen the glass sliding door leads to the screened-in lanai where you can sit back relax and unwind with your morning coffee or evening cocktail, with a lake-view from the lanai and your FENCED in backyard. The spacious Owner’s En-suite has a large walk-in closet, gorgeous bathroom which features quartz countertop, dual sinks and a tiled walk-in shower. The split floor plan offers a sense of privacy to your guests with a bedroom and beautiful guest bathroom with a tub/shower combo and quartz countertop. The nicely appointed den with glass french doors and a window allows for lots of natural sunlight. The home features a large interior laundry room with high-end washer/dryer and a 2-car garage with storage shelves. Toscana Isles is an active lifestyle community that includes an absolutely breathtaking 8,000 Sq/ft Clubhouse with highly sought-after state of the art amenities such as an infinity pool, fitness room, party room, billiard room w/bar & big screen TV. There is also a screened terrace, pickle ball, tennis and bocce ball courts, dog park, playground, fishing, kayaking and canoeing, all on 200 acres of interconnected lakes within the community. Toscana Isles has low HOA’s and is PET FRIENDLY. Conveniently located, close to I-75, beautiful Historical Downtown Venice, fabulous beaches, The Legacy Bike Trail, Atlanta Braves Practice Stadium, Downtown Wellen Park. You will also find plenty of restaurants, terrific shopping and the New Sarasota Memorial Hospital. Put this HOME on your MUST-SEE list!! Call today for your private showing.
